doctype html
head
  meta(charset='UTF-8')
  meta(name='viewport' content='width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0')
  title Flo Mindrise - About Us
  link(rel='stylesheet' href='styles/about.css')
header
  nav
    ul
      li
        a(href='/') Home
      li
        a(href='/about') About Us
      li
        a(href='/contact') Contact
main
  section.about-header
    h1 About Flo Mindrise
    p
      | Flo Mindrise is a mental wellness platform designed to help individuals cultivate positive thinking, improve emotional resilience, and empower youth to believe in their potential.
  section.cards-container
    // Mission Card
    .card
      .card-image
        img(src='https://www.malvernbh.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/shutterstock_1449672365-min-1-scaled.jpg' alt='Mission Image')
      .card-content
        h2 Mission
        p
          | Our mission is to empower individuals to achieve mental wellness through practical tools, personalized support, and a positive community. We strive to help everyone tap into their full potential, embrace growth, and foster a mindset that thrives.
    // Vision Card
    .card.reverse
      .card-image.circular-frame
        img(src='https://images.pexels.com/photos/3184465/pexels-photo-3184465.jpeg' alt='Vision Image')
      .card-content
        h2 Vision Statement
        p
          | We envision a world where every young person has the mental tools and confidence to succeed and overcome life&rsquo;s challenges.
  
    .card
      .card-image
        img(src='https://images.pexels.com/photos/3184292/pexels-photo-3184292.jpeg' alt='Core Values Image')
      .card-content
        h2 Core Values
        ul
          li
            strong Empathy
            |  - Understanding the unique needs of each individual.
          li
            strong Inspiration
            |  - Providing motivational content and success stories.
          li
            strong Growth
            |  - Empowering youth to develop positive mindsets and resilience.
          li
            strong Community
            |  - Building a supportive environment for users to connect.
    // Problem Card
    .card.reverse
      .card-image.circular-frame
        img(src='https://images.pexels.com/photos/3184396/pexels-photo-3184396.jpeg' alt='Problem Image')
      .card-content
        h2 The Problem We Are Solving
        p
          | In a world where mental health is often overlooked, especially among youth, Flo Mindrise provides a safe space and tools to navigate challenges, reduce stress, and foster a positive mindset.
    // Approach Card
    .card
      .card-image
        img(src='https://images.pexels.com/photos/3182820/pexels-photo-3182820.jpeg' alt='Approach Image')
      .card-content
        h2 Our Approach
        p
          | Through daily affirmations, guided meditations, success stories, and expert advice, Flo Mindrise guides individuals on their journey towards mental wellness.
  section.cta
    h2 Join the Movement
    p
      | Join us on the journey to a brighter future. Start your mental wellness journey today with Flo Mindrise.
    a.cta-button(href='/addUser') Sign Up Now
